[[File:KX-80_Repeating_Blaster_Rifle.jpg|thumb|right|A KX-80 Repeating Blaster Rifle.]]
The [[Kashnir Arms]] '''KX-80 repeating [[Blaster rifle/Legends|blaster rifle]]''' was originally intended as a squad-level infantry support weapon. It was developed during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]] under contract for several world defense arms, and there was only ever a limited prototype production run made. The increasing number of these weapons in the hands of the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] was proof that [[Kashnir Arms]] were operating once more after the [[Imperial Security Bureau/Legends|ISB]] shut their factories down, now under Alliance direction.

